{"tid":330003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（博盡無悔。抗爭零成本）馮敬恩面臨判監","createTime":"2017-07-20T21:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T05:13:13.000Z","uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"673fe00774cb7b729b0d1945c62b90d605cf23d0","tid":330003,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T21:40:58.000Z","msg":"去年1月26日香港大學校務委員會討論學生提出的改革訴求，會後校委遭學生包圍要求對話，擾攘至凌晨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裁判官昨裁定馮恐嚇罪不成立，因不肯定隊冧「佢」是否說給李國章聽，但裁定交替性的擾亂秩序罪成立。同被控的副會長李峰琦則被裁定阻礙公職人員罪成。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裁判官押後判刑，先索取報告並准兩被告保釋，但強調案情嚴重，判監可能性相當高。"},{"pid":"e3cde5f9ab2cbf03ee82ef0a42bb6e099456f32d","tid":330003,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T22:58:34.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"4bf00f5fbb9cb2cd219e191ac3671e256d87eabc","tid":330003,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:02:44.000Z","msg":"香港已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9a0069243951c7177cda8a48909355eea5901d","tid":330003,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:40:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e202fdb3ae9bea75da927e2ead9a09bd6eefc31f","tid":330003,"uid":15249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:43:27.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心想知有幾嚴重"},{"pid":"3cef88723aef2e7989db81285bc928f4c47e411d","tid":330003,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:43:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有幾嚴重❓</blockquote><br />\n你嚇親權貴，罪大當誅"},{"pid":"2ce99488899959f4c2594ef8c119443fee3b24d9","tid":330003,"uid":10520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:47:17.000Z","msg":"咁就一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{